        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "PSALM 99: 1-5, 9\nADONAI MALACH yirg'zu amim,\nyosheiv k'ruvim tanut haaretz.\nAdonai b'Tzion gadol\nv'ram hu al kol haamim.\nYodu shimcha gadol v'nora,\nkadosh hu.\nV'oz Melech mishpat aheiv,\natah konanta meisharim,\nmishpat utz’dakah b'Yaakov\natah asita.\nRom'mu Adonai Eloheinu\nv'hishtachavu lahadom raglav,\nkadosh hu.\nRom'mu Adonai Eloheinu\nv'hishtachavu l'har kodsho,\nki kadosh Adonai Eloheinu.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-14T17:47:56.374Z",
